Geographical distribution . The species spreads from Mar del Plata (
Blanco 1967 b
) southwards to Tierra del Fuego (
Hartlaub 1901
,
Jäderholm 1903
,
Billard 1922
,
Naumov & Stepanjants 1962
). Additional subantarctic records are from around the Falkland Islands (
Lamouroux 1824
,
Meyen 1834
,
El Beshbeeshy 2011
), the Kerguelen and Crozet shelves (
Millard 1977
), and from off Bouvet Is. (
Peña Cantero & Gili 2006
). Antarctic records are from the South Shetland islands (
Stepanjants 1979
; Peña Cantero 2006, 2009; present study), off Low Is. (
Blanco 1984
;
Peña Cantero & Vervoort 2009
), Trinity Is. (
Peña Cantero 2008
), Booth (Wandel) Is. (
Billard 1906
), Bellinghausen Sea (
Peña Cantero 2012
).
